        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your molecular structure is more resistant to certain damage types. You gain additional resistance to the damage type chosen with @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Molecular Modification]. Your resistance to the chosen damage type equals your level, instead of half your level.</p><hr /><p><strong>Special</strong> If you've taken Molecular Modification multiple times, you can take this feat multiple times, each time gaining additional resistance to a different damage type chosen with Molecular Modification.</p>"
